title: Wings Over America (2013 Deluxe Remaster + Cow Palace/DVD)
description:
*** NOTICE *** NOTICE *** NOTICE***

In the interest of being clear as to the source of the material here, please note the following: discs 1, 2, and 3 are straight from the Archive Collection remaster of Wings Over America. This particular set was purchased at the American electronics store, Best Buy (thus the Cow Palace bonus disc). However, the Wings Over the World documentary on disc 4 IS NOT FROM AN ACTUAL DVD FROM THE BOX SET. Since I haven't been able to find an upload of the bonus DVD to share, I have instead place a TV rip of a BBC airing of the documentary. You will notice a little BBC mark in the top left corner of the screen. I assure you that this special is frame for frame exactly what you would find on the box set DVD. I'll piss off now, enjoy the material. 


*** ALL TRACKS 320KBPS/16 BIT MP3 ***

*** ALL TAGS (ARTIST, YEAR, NAME, ALBUM, ETC.) EMBEDDED
